Class TrackingBase

Direct Known Subclasses:
EmailCampaignTrackingBounce, EmailCampaignTrackingClick, EmailCampaignTrackingForward, EmailCampaignTrackingOpen, EmailCampaignTrackingSend, EmailCampaignTrackingUnsubscribe, TrackingContactsBase
public class TrackingBase
extends Component
implements Serializable

Base class for all the Email Campaign Tracking classes used by the Email Campaign Tracking Service in Constant Contact.
Base class for all the Contact Tracking classes used by the Contact Tracking Service in Constant Contact.
It defines the common fields:

  • Contact Id
  • Activity Type
  • Campaign Id
  • Email Address
Each sub-class will come with a particular value for Activity Type, depending on the answer type.
Each sub-class will also add its own new fields, depending on the business logic.

ConstantContact
